Ext.data.JsonP['Global_Styles']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Global Styles</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-41845687\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Global Styles</h1>\n    <p>Demonstrates using the global style file to apply a set of default styles to an entire Alloy project.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox admonition admonition-info aui-message hint shadowed information-macro\">\n            <div class=\"title\">App Folder Location</div>\n            <p>alloy/test/apps/<strong class=\" \">basics/global_style</strong>    </p>\n    </div>\n        <img src=\"images/download/attachments/41845687/ios.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/41845687/ios.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"250\">\n        <p>An Alloy project can include a <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/guide/Alloy_Styles_and_Themes-section-35621526_AlloyStylesandThemes-GlobalStyles\">global style file</a> located at app/styles/app.tss. The styles defined by this file apply to all controls and views, but are over-ridden by &quot;local&quot; styles declared by the following:    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>ID or class styles declared by a controller styles (views/index.tss, for example).    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Styles assigned directly to an XML element    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>In this example, the main <strong class=\" \">index.xml</strong> view requires <strong class=\" \">item.xml.</strong>    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                    <div class=\"title\">app/views/index.xml</div>\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\" data-title=\"app/views/index.xml\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;Window&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;Require src=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;item&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;/Window&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <p>The item.xml view contains a &lt;View/&gt; element whose &quot;class&quot; attribute is set to &quot;container&quot;.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                    <div class=\"title\">app/views/item.xml</div>\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\" data-title=\"app/views/item.xml\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;View </code><code class=\"keyword\">class</code><code class=\"plain\">=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;container&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;Label id=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;label&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;should be bold, red text on blue background&lt;/Label&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;/View&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <p>The global style file defines a blue <tt class=\" \">backgroundColor</tt> to the &quot;container&quot; class, and a color, font size and weight, and text alignment for all Label objects.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                    <div class=\"title\">styles/app.tss</div>\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\" data-title=\"styles/app.tss\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"string\">&quot;.container&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">: {</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  backgroundColor: </code><code class=\"string\">&quot;#00f&quot;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">}</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"string\">&quot;Label&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">: {</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  color: </code><code class=\"string\">&quot;#f00&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">,</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  font: {</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    fontSize: </code><code class=\"value\">24</code><code class=\"plain\">,</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    fontWeight: </code><code class=\"string\">&apos;bold&apos;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  },</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  textAlign: </code><code class=\"string\">&apos;center&apos;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">}</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-41845687_GlobalStyles-SeeAlso\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>See Also</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link unresolved\" href=\"#!/guide/Global_Styles-section-src-41845687\">Global Styles</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Custom_TSS_Queries\">Custom TSS Queries</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>    </p>\n    </div>\n        </img></div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=41845687\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Global Styles"});